BARENTS SEA.
NORWEGIAN SEA.
MANDATORY SHIP REPORTING SYSTEM.
THE MARITIME SAFETY COMMITTEE (IMO) WILL IMPLEMENT
A NEW MANDATORY SHIP REPORTING SYSTEM IN THE
BARENTS SEA AREA AT 010001Z JUN 2013. INFORMATION
ABOUT THE REPORTING SYSTEM CAN BE FOUND IN
IMO ANNEX 27, RESOLUTION MSC.348(91) AND
NORWEGIAN NOTICE TO MARINERS 8 AND 9/13.
